OL,3,CLabour offers to meet JK Rowling to
OL,4,Cgive 'assurances' on women's rights
OL,6,FLabour says it will make it easier for
OL,7,Fpeople to legally change genders, ITV
OL,8,FNews Political Correspondent Carl
OL,9,FDinnen reports from the campaign trail.
OL,11,FLabour's Rachel Reeves says the party
OL,12,Fwill meet with Harry Potter author JK
OL,13,FRowling to give her "assurances" over
OL,14,Fthe party's commitment to protecting
OL,15,Fwomen-only spaces.
OL,17,FThe shadow chancellor made the offer
OL,18,Fafter Rowling said at the weekend that
OL,19,FLabour had "abandoned" her and others
OL,20,Fcampaigning for women's rights.
