OL,3,CLabour offers to meet JK Rowling to
OL,4,Cgive 'assurances' on women's rights
OL,6,FReeves, however, insisted protection
OL,7,Ffor single-sex spaces for women would
OL,8,F"absolutely stay".
OL,10,FSpeaking as she campaigned in
OL,11,FScotland, Reeves said: "We're not
OL,12,Fgoing to be changing anything around
OL,13,Fbiological sex. So the Equality Act
OL,14,Fstands and the protection of single-
OL,15,Fsex spaces, based on biological sex
OL,16,Fwill absolutely stay.
OL,18,F"Labour introduced the Equality Act,
OL,19,Fit is very important to us and that
OL,20,Fprotection for single-sex spaces."
