OL,6,FRegarding Rowling's comments, the
OL,7,Fshadow chancellor added: "We're really
OL,8,Fhappy to talk to JK Rowling to give
OL,9,Fher assurances about that."
OL,11,FReeves insisted: "For me, those
OL,12,Fprotections whether it is about
OL,13,Fprisons, refuges, changing spaces,
OL,14,Fthat is really important to me, it is
OL,15,Freally important to the Labour Party
OL,16,Fthat those single-sex spaces based on
OL,17,Fbiological sex are protected.
OL,19,F"And nothing in our plans goes
OL,20,Fcontrary to that, nothing at all."
