OL,6,FLabour's Shadow Health Secretary Wes
OL,7,FStreeting said the debate around
OL,8,Ftransgender and women's rights is
OL,9,Foften "toxic".
OL,11,F"There will be spaces that will be
OL,12,Fonly for biological women, those
OL,13,Fspaces need to be protected, their
OL,14,Fvoices need to be respected and
OL,15,Fprotected," he said.
OL,17,F"We're confident that we can find our
OL,18,Fway through what has actually been
OL,19,Foften a toxic discussion."
